7 A Joint Resolution approving proposed permanent rules
of certain state health-related agencies; excluding
8 certain proposed rules of the Oklahoma Health Care
Authority; and directing distribution.
9
10
11 WHEREAS, pursuant to Section 308 of Title 75 of the Oklahoma
12 Statutes, the Oklahoma State Legislature shall adopt a joint
13 resolution to approve or disapprove administrative rules.
14 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
15 AND THE SENATE OF THE 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
16 SECTION 1. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
17 permanent rules of the State Board of Behavioral Health Licensure
18 filed on or before February 1, 2026.
19 SECTION 2. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
20 permanent rules of the Oklahoma Health Care Authority filed on or
21 before February 1, 2026, except for the following: OAC 317:30-3-57,
22 317:30-3-59, 317:30-5-2, 317:30-5-9, 317:30-5-10, 317:30-5-11,
23 317:30-5-15, 317:30-5-42.4, 317:30-5-47, 317:30-5-47.7, 317:30-5-
24 261, 317:30-5-354, 317:30-5-355.2, 317:30-5-356, 317:30-5-359.2,
