3 SECTION 3. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
4 permanent rules of the Department of Human Services filed on or
5 before February 1, 2026.
6 SECTION 4. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
7 permanent rules of the State Board of Medical Licensure and
8 Supervision filed on or before February 1, 2026.
9 SECTION 5. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
10 permanent rules of the Department of Mental Health and Substance
11 Abuse Services filed on or before February 1, 2026.
12 SECTION 6. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
13 permanent rules of the Oklahoma Board of Nursing filed on or before
14 February 1, 2026.
15 SECTION 7. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
16 permanent rules of the Board of Examiners in Optometry filed on or
17 before February 1, 2026.
18 SECTION 8. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
19 permanent rules of the State Board of Osteopathic Examiners filed on
20 or before February 1, 2026.
21 SECTION 9. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
22 permanent rules of the Oklahoma State Board of Pharmacy filed on or
23 before February 1, 2026.
