1 SECTION 10. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
2 permanent rules of the Health Care Workforce Training Commission
3 filed on or before February 1, 2026.
4 SECTION 11. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
5 permanent rules of the State Department of Rehabilitation Services
6 filed on or before February 1, 2026.
7 SECTION 12. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
8 permanent rules of the Board of Examiners for Speech-Language
9 Pathology and Audiology filed on or before February 1, 2026.
10 SECTION 13. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
11 permanent rules of the University Hospitals Authority filed on or
12 before February 1, 2026.
13 SECTION 14. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
14 permanent rules of the University Hospitals Trust filed on or before
15 February 1, 2026.
16 SECTION 15. The Oklahoma Secretary of State is hereby directed
17 to distribute copies of this resolution to the Governor and the
18 editor of "The Oklahoma Register".
